  "description": "This dataset contains multimodal neuroimaging data from a study investigating the neural mechanisms of expectation and conflict processing. The research examines how the brain anticipates and responds to conflicting stimuli using simultaneous fMRI and EEG recordings. The dataset includes anatomical MRI, functional MRI, fieldmaps, and concurrent EEG data, with potential implications for understanding cognitive control and decision-making processes.",
